messages.message: @shaunak just following up on this to see if we were able to get anything going via the release scan pipeline to include image license details? If nothing is in yet, can you help to review this list (https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1XDoyV28ibBB1lCG2kl42MSaFp3INU_gTtBF1hgItvEk/edit#gid=1766344109) and confirm if this can be sent across to HSBC?
Yeah we were able to get this @Varun Rao. @sreeraj added in a functionality to include this in release scans, and we need to merge this in. He can help you with details/ info you need here.
Thanks @sudeep for confirming! @sreeraj when you see this, it would be great to see what I can forward over to HSBC.

@Varun Rao for 22.08.0 (https://release-scans.s3.amazonaws.com/2022-08-10/22.08.0-scan-results.xlsx?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Credential=AKIAX7YFPI7G7JZEYAFG%2F20220810%2Fus-east-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20220810T152623Z&X-Amz-Expires=604800&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&X-Amz-Signature=577ea3064bc2de8251e9741977920adfbac8f3879648bcebfa49f605543a9b77) => look for resources sheet at the end which has license details.
